# Haskell Tools Hlint

Hlint is a style checking tool. Together with *apply-refact* it updates haskell source files automatically.

### Usage

~~~
hlint --refactor myfile.hs
~~~

Add an refactor option of -s to be prompted for each change

~~~
hlint -- refactor --refactor-options="-s" myfile.hs
~~~

